'''Op-die-Berg''' ke toropo nyanenyane wa [[Witzenberg Mmusogae|Witzenberg]], [[Mmasepala Setereke tša Cape Winelands]] go feta [[Kapa Bodikela]] ka moka [[Afrika Borwa]].

It is located north of [[Ceres]] in the Kouebokkeveld region, synonymous with cherry orchards and occasional heavy snowfalls in winter. 

